body: "Authoritative scope is Monica stable 4.x routes/api.php at commit 32028ce3ce79cef38df5d27a297e5b20680f0065 plus official API docs. Implement missing statistics, places, life events, upcoming reminders, and me-contact association; reconcile contact action route variants; keep all live proof GET-only under read-only mode; preserve schema-valid agent outputs and complete help/docs."
